Package: privacyguardian
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: PrivacyGuardian Team
Installed-Size: 500
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-venv, python3-gi, python3-gi-cairo, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, libsodium23, curl
Section: net
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/Keeper888/privacyguardian
Description: Universal LLM PII Protection
 PrivacyGuardian protects your personal information when using
 AI assistants like Claude, ChatGPT, and Cursor by encrypting
 sensitive data before it leaves your device.
 .
 Features:
  - 35+ PII types detected (emails, SSN, credit cards, health data, etc.)
  - Local encryption - AI sees tokens, you see real data
  - Works with any LLM: Anthropic, OpenAI, Google, Azure, Mistral
  - GTK4 GUI dashboard for easy control
